---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="IBC Academy is an education-first platform teaching the Infinite Banking Concept based on Nelson Nash's Becoming Your Own Banker. No products sold. No financial advice. Just transformation through education.">

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO — "About IBC Academy"
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="fade-in-up">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gold/10 border border-gold/20 mb-6">
          <span class="text-gold text-sm font-medium">Education First</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
          About <span class="text-gold">IBC Academy</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl sm:text-2xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          We don't sell financial products. We don't give financial advice. We teach the Infinite Banking Concept — clearly, honestly, and for free.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       MISSION
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in-up">
        <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 text-center">
          <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              IBC Academy exists to provide free, rigorous education on Nelson Nash's Infinite Banking Concept as taught in <em class="text-white">Becoming Your Own Banker</em>. We believe the banking function is the most important financial concept most people never learn — and that understanding it changes everything.
            </p>
            <blockquote class="relative">
              <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-gold/30 text-6xl font-serif">"</div>
              <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-gold italic leading-relaxed pt-4">
                We're not here to sell you something.<br />
                We're here to teach you something.
              </p>
            </blockquote>
            <p class="mt-8 text-slate-300">
              We chose transformation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       WHAT IBC ACADEMY IS / IS NOT
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in-up text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white">
          Clarity on <span class="text-gold">Who We Are</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- What We ARE -->
        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">What IBC Academy Is</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300">An <strong class="text-white">educational platform</strong> teaching the Infinite Banking Concept as Nelson Nash described it</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300"><strong class="text-white">Purely educational.</strong> Free courses, articles, and community discussion</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300">Aligned with the teachings of <strong class="text-white">Nelson Nash, Robert Murphy, Carlos Lara,</strong> and <strong class="text-white">James Neathery</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300">Built on the conviction that <strong class="text-white">understanding banking changes lives</strong> — and that understanding should be accessible to everyone</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- What We ARE NOT -->
        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-500/15 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">What IBC Academy Is Not</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400/70 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300"><strong class="text-white">Not a sales platform.</strong> We don't sell insurance policies, investments, or financial products of any kind</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400/70 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300"><strong class="text-white">Not financial advice.</strong> Nothing on this site constitutes a recommendation to purchase any financial product</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400/70 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300"><strong class="text-white">Not affiliated</strong> with any insurance company, broker-dealer, or financial services firm</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400/70 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-slate-300"><strong class="text-white">Not a shortcut.</strong> IBC requires study, discipline, and honest thinking — we won't pretend otherwise</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE TEACHING APPROACH
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in-up text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white">
          How We <span class="text-gold">Teach</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Nelson Nash said if you understand the grocery store, the rest is "a piece of cake." We take the same approach — concept first, mechanics second.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 stagger-children">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-gold font-extrabold text-lg">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">The Banking Function</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Everything starts here. Banking is the most important business in the world — without it, all commerce stops. You finance everything you buy: either you pay interest to someone else, or you give up the interest you could have earned. There is no third option. We teach you to see this invisible flow.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-gold font-extrabold text-lg">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">The Mechanics</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Once you understand <em>why</em> the banking function matters, we show you <em>how</em> dividend-paying whole life insurance serves as the chassis for your personal banking system. Cash value, policy loans, dividends, paid-up additions — the machinery that makes it work.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-gold font-extrabold text-lg">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Compared to What?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Every financial decision is a comparison. We examine IBC against the alternatives — 401(k)s, term insurance, "buy term and invest the difference," market investing — not with sales pitches, but with honest analysis. Nash's question was always: <em>compared to what?</em>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-gold font-extrabold text-lg">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Real-World Application</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Theory without application is incomplete. We walk through real scenarios — financing equipment, buying vehicles, funding businesses, building multi-generational wealth. Not hypotheticals. The same situations Nash's grocery store analogy was designed to illuminate.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE IBC LINEAGE
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in-up text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white">
          The IBC <span class="text-gold">Lineage</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          IBC Academy teaches from a lineage. These are the thinkers whose work forms the foundation of everything we present.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Nelson Nash -->
        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">R. Nelson Nash</h3>
              <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium mb-3">Creator of the Infinite Banking Concept</p>
              <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                Nelson Nash discovered IBC during a personal financial crisis in 1980 — owing $500,000 at 23% interest while his family endured one catastrophe after another. The answer, he later wrote, hit him "like a baseball bat across the eyes." His book <em class="text-white">Becoming Your Own Banker</em> is the definitive source text. Nash spent the rest of his life teaching that banking is the most important business in the world, and that ordinary people can — and should — control the banking function in their own lives. Everything at IBC Academy traces back to his work.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Murphy & Lara -->
        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Robert P. Murphy & L. Carlos Lara</h3>
              <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium mb-3">Austrian Economics & the LMR Newsletter</p>
              <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                Murphy and Lara brought rigorous Austrian economic theory to the IBC conversation. Their <em class="text-white">Lara-Murphy Report</em> (LMR) newsletter connected Nash's practical insights to the deeper economic principles that explain <em>why</em> the banking function works the way it does. Murphy's work on free-market economics and Lara's expertise in privatized banking gave IBC its intellectual foundation beyond the mechanics — grounding it in sound money, savings-driven growth, and the critique of fractional-reserve banking.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- James Neathery -->
        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">James Neathery</h3>
              <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium mb-3">Authorized IBC Practitioner & Mentor</p>
              <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                James Neathery was mentored directly by Nelson Nash himself. When Brad completed the Nelson Nash Institute's Practitioner program, James graciously took him under his wing — passing on not just the mechanics of IBC, but the philosophy and discipline that Nash instilled in his own students. This mentor-to-mentee chain represents the way IBC was meant to be taught: person to person, principle before product, with patience and integrity.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Brad Raschke / IBC Academy -->
        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10 border-gold/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/5 to-transparent">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-gold-dark flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-navy-900 font-black text-2xl">B</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Brad Raschke & IBC Academy</h3>
              <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium mb-3">Authorized IBC Practitioner & Founder</p>
              <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                I discovered IBC in 2015 through the Lara-Murphy Report podcast during a 3-year deep dive into Austrian economics that started with Ron Paul. After completing the Nelson Nash Institute's Practitioner program and being mentored by James Neathery, I built IBC Academy to provide the kind of rigorous, education-first content I wished had existed when I was learning. No products for sale here — just the concepts, the mechanics, and the honest answers to the questions everyone asks.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       ABOUT THE FOUNDER
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in-up">
        <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 border-gold/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/5 to-transparent">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center md:items-start">
            <!-- Founder Avatar -->
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl shadow-gold/20">
                <img src="/images/brad-raschke.jpg" alt="Brad Raschke" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Founder Info -->
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
              <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
                About the <span class="text-gold">Founder</span>
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gold text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Brad Raschke — Authorized IBC Practitioner</p>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  A Texan by birth, I graduated from Howard Payne University with a BA in US History in December 2012. During my senior year, a 3-year "Ron Paul rabbit hole" eventually led me to discover the Infinite Banking Concept in 2015.
                </p>
                <p>
                  In the middle of a budding career at a stockholding, IUL-focused insurance company, the truths of IBC and the potential of dividend-paying whole life convicted me. I left my job to pursue practicing IBC with my clients the right way — education first, relationships second, business as a natural result.
                </p>
                <p>
                  After completing the Nelson Nash Institute's Practitioner program, James Neathery graciously took me under his wing and mentored me, just as Nelson Nash mentored James. That lineage matters to me.
                </p>
                <p>
                  I married my wife, Hailey, in March 2020. Our son, Declan Mac, was born in March 2021, and we currently live in Geneva, Illinois. My pursuit of truth, love of people, and faith in Christ inform every interaction and relationship with my clients.
                </p>
                <p>
                  I built IBC Academy because most IBC content online is either oversimplified marketing or buried in jargon. People deserve better — <em class="text-white">concept first, mechanics second</em>. No products for sale here. Just transformation through education.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4">
                <a
                  href="/contact"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gold text-navy-900 font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-gold-light transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-gold/20"
                >
                  Schedule a Conversation
                  <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
